STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Wukeem W. LEWIS, a/k/a Wallace W. Lewis, and Wakeem Lewis, Defendant-Petitioner. C-498 September Term 2018
081470 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 18, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001711-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
